+Kaoutzanis&amp;author=AM+Carbonell&amp;author=MG+Franz&amp;publication_year=2015&amp;journal=World+J+Gastrointest+Surg&amp;pages=293-305&amp;doi=10.4240%2Fwjgs.v7.i11.293&amp;pmid=26649152">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Aguirre DA, Santosa AC, Casola G, Sirlin CB. Abdominal wall hernias: imaging features, complications, and diagnostic pitfalls at multi-detector row CT. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2005;25(6):1501–1520.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.256055018">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16284131/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Abdominal+wall+hernias%3A+imaging+features%2C+complications%2C+and+diagnostic+pitfalls+at+multi-detector+row+CT&amp;author=DA+Aguirre&amp;author=AC+Santosa&amp;author=G+Casola&amp;author=CB+Sirlin&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1501-1520&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.256055018&amp;pmid=16284131">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">13.</div><div id="r13" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Levy S, Moszkowicz D, Poghosyan T, et al. Comparison of complete versus partial mesh removal for the treatment of chronic mesh infection after abdominal wall hernia repair. <em>Hernia</em> 2018;22(5):773–779.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s10029-018-1785-1">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29796848/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Comparison+of+complete+versus+p